data.description: New Listing! Beautifully updated and well cared for 4 bedroom, 3 bath, Two Story home located just minutes from downtown, Lauritzen Gardens, the Henry Doorly Zoo and easy access to I -80 and many new restaurants on 16th St! Step right into a move-in-ready home! All new kitchen with gas range in 2018 and ALL appliances stay! New bathrooms in 2018, A/C in 2018 (just serviced), Furnace in 2018 (just serviced), new roof in 2018 and many other tasteful updates. Relax in the back yard with a new deck a 6’ privacy fence or on the new front porch. This home is on a HUGE corner with lot plenty of room to add an outbuilding or garage. A home in this price range won’t last long so schedule a tour ASAP!
